data.description: Nestled behind ancient Live oak trees, this well-maintained older manufactured home offers a unique blend of natural beauty, accessibility, and comfort. A fenced yard, handicap ramp, and versatile pole barn enhance the property's appeal. Inside, open living space, cozy bedrooms, and upgraded kitchen cabinets provide comfort, making it an inviting haven for all. All furniture will remain with the home. The property is completely fenced and cross-fenced and in mostly pasture, so farm animals are welcome!
